A pair of conjoined twins promise each other that they will always be together. Mysterious circumstances lead to the death of one, while the other survives. The ghost of the dead comes back to haunt the surviving sister.
A man marries three different women who live in the same building and are unaware that they have the same husband. To make matters worse, all his wives get invited to his fourth wedding.

An aspiring actor falls in love with Kavya, a doctor. Upon knowing that she's already engaged, he disguises himself as a female nurse with the aim of breaking her engagement.
Hari, a young DJ, keeps getting rejected by every girl he proposes to. When he faces another brutal rejection by Sailaja, a girl he truly loves, he sets out to change her mind.

A chief minister's son leads a double life as a gangster who helps wealthy wrongdoers escape the law. His atrocities catch up to him in the form of an army veteran, who enjoys playing a vigilante.
A look at the youth of the late 2010s, and how they navigate the mixture of reality and digital created by the phenomenon of social media.
